\c 21
\s UAhabi lesivini sikaNabothi
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi emva kwalezizinto uNabothi umJizereyeli wayelesivini esasiseJizereyeli\x + Josh. 17.16.\x* phansi kwesigodlo sikaAhabi inkosi yeSamariya.
\v 2 UAhabi wasekhuluma loNabothi esithi: Ngipha isivini sakho ukuze sibe kimi yisivande semibhida, ngoba siseduze phansi kwendlu yami; ngizakunika isivini esingcono kulaso esikhundleni saso; uba kukuhle emehlweni akho, ngizakunika imali ngentengo yaso\x + 1 Sam. 8.14.\x*.
\v 3 Kodwa uNabothi wathi kuAhabi: Kakube khatshana lami ngeN\nd kosi\nd* ukuthi ngikunike ilifa labobaba\x + Levi 25.23. Nani 36.7. Hez. 46.18.\x*.
\v 4 UAhabi wasengena endlini yakhe enyukumele ethukuthele ngenxa yelizwi uNabothi umJizereyeli ayelikhulume kuye, ngoba wayethe: Kangiyikukunika ilifa labobaba. Wasecambalala embhedeni wakhe, waphendula ubuso bakhe, kadlanga ukudla\x + 20.43.\x*.
\p
\v 5 UJezebeli umkakhe wasesiza kuye wathi kuye: Kungani umoya wakho usineme ukuze ungadli ukudla?
\v 6 Wasesithi kuye: Ngoba ngikhulume loNabothi umJizereyeli ngithe kuye: Nginike isivini sakho ngemali, loba uba uthanda ngizakunika isivini esikhundleni saso; wasesithi: Kangiyikukunika isivini sami.
\v 7 UJezebeli umkakhe wasesithi kuye: Khathesi nguwe obusa umbuso wakoIsrayeli? Vuka udle isinkwa, lenhliziyo yakho ithokoze; ngizakunika mina isivini sikaNabothi umJizereyeli\x + 8.66.\x*.
\v 8 Wasebhala izincwadi ngebizo likaAhabi, wazidinda ngophawu lwakhe\x + Esta 3.12.\x*, wazithumela izincwadi ebadaleni lakuzikhulu, ababesemzini wakhe, behlala loNabothi\x + 21.11. 20.7. Ruthe 4.2.\x*.
\v 9 Wasebhala ezincwadini esithi: Memezelani izilo lokudla, limhlalise uNabothi ngaphezulu kwabantu;
\v 10 beselihlalisa amadoda amabili, amadodana kaBheliyali, maqondana laye ukuthi afakaze emelene laye\x + Dute. 13.13.\x* esithi: Uthuke\x + Eks. 22.28. Levi 24.16. Seb. 6.11.\x* uNkulunkulu lenkosi\x + 21.13. Jobe 1.5,11. 2.5, 9.\x*. Beselimkhuphela phandle limkhande ngamatshe aze afe.
\v 11 Lamadoda alumuzi wakhe, abadala lezikhulu ababehlala emzini wakhe, benza njengokuthumela kukaJezebeli kuwo, njengokubhalwe ezincwadini ayewathumele zona.
\v 12 Amemezela izilo lokudla, ahlalisa uNabothi phezulu kwabantu\x + Isa. 58.4,5.\x*.
\v 13 Asengena amadoda amabili, amadodana kaBheliyali, ahlala maqondana laye; lamadoda kaBheliyali afakaza emelene laye, emelene loNabothi, phambi kwabantu\x + 21.11. 20.7. Ruthe 4.2.\x*, esithi: UNabothi uthuke uNkulunkulu lenkosi\x + 21.13. Jobe 1.5,11. 2.5,9.\x*. Basebemkhuphela ngaphandle komuzi, bamkhanda ngamatshe waze wafa.
\v 14 Basebethumela kuJezebeli besithi: UNabothi usekhandwe ngamatshe wafa.
\p
\v 15 Kwasekusithi uJezebeli esezwile ukuthi uNabothi usekhandwe ngamatshe wafa, uJezebeli wathi kuAhabi: Vuka uthathe isivini sikaNabothi umJizereyeli sibe ngesakho, ala ukukunika sona ngemali, ngoba uNabothi kaphili, kodwa ufile.
\v 16 Kwasekusithi uAhabi esezwile ukuthi uNabothi ufile, uAhabi wasukuma ukwehlela esivinini sikaNabothi umJizereyeli, ukusithatha sibe ngesakhe.
\p
\v 17 Kwasekufika ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* kuElija\x + Hlab. 9.12.\x* umTishibi\x + 21.28. 17.1. 2 Kho. 1.3,8. 9.36.\x* lisithi:
\v 18 Sukuma wehle ukuhlangabeza uAhabi inkosi yakoIsrayeli, oseSamariya\x + 21.43. 16.24.\x*; khangela, usesivinini sikaNabothi, ehlele khona ukuze asithathe sibe ngesakhe.
\v 19 Uzakhuluma kuye uthi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ubulele futhi wathatha yini kwaba ngokwakho? Njalo uzakhuluma kuye uthi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Endaweni lapho izinja ezikhothe khona igazi likaNabothi, izinja zizakhotha igazi lakho, ngitsho elakho\x + 22.38. 2 Kho. 9.26.\x*.
\v 20 UAhabi wasesithi kuElija: Ungificile yini, sitha sami\x + 18.17.\x*? Wasesithi: Ngi\add ku\add*tholile, ngoba uzithengisile ukwenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 21.25. 2 Kho. 17.17. Roma 7.14.\x*.
\v 21 Khangela, ngizakwehlisela ububi\x + 14.10. 2 Kho. 9.8.\x*, ngiqothule inzalo yakho\x + 16.3.\x*, ngiqume asuke kuAhabi ochamela emdulini\x + 1 Sam. 25.22.\x*, lovalelweyo lokhululekileyo koIsrayeli\x + Dute. 32.36.\x*.
\v 22 Njalo ngizakwenza indlu yakho ibe njengendlu kaJerobhowamu indodana kaNebati\x + 15.29.\x* lanjengendlu kaBahasha indodana kaAhiya\x + 16.3,11.\x*, ngenxa yesicunulo o\add ngi\add*cunule ngaso, wenza uIsrayeli one\x + 14.16.\x*.
\v 23 LangoJezebeli laye iN\nd kosi\nd* yakhuluma isithi: Izinja zizamudla uJezebeli emthangaleni weJizereyeli\x + 2 Kho. 9.36.\x*.
\v 24 OkaAhabi ofela phakathi komuzi zizamudla izinja, lofela egangeni zizamudla inyoni zamazulu\x + 14.11.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Kodwa kakubanga khona onjengoAhabi\x + 16.30-33.\x* owazithengisa ukwenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 21.20.\x*, uJezebeli umkakhe amkhuthazayo.
\v 26 Wenza amanyala kakhulu ngokulandela izithombe\x + 15.12. 2 Kho. 17.12. 21.11. Dute. 29.17.\x*, njengakho konke amaAmori akwenzayo\x + Gen. 15.16. 2 Kho. 21.11.\x*, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyawaxotsha elifeni phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\p
\v 27 Kwasekusithi uAhabi esizwa lamazwi wadabula izigqoko zakhe\x + 2 Kho. 6.30. Gen. 44.13.\x*, wafaka isaka phezu komzimba wakhe\x + 20.31.\x*, wazila ukudla\x + 2 Sam. 12.16.\x*, walala ngesaka, wahamba buthakathaka.
\v 28 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kuElija umTishibi lisithi:
\v 29 Ubonile yini ukuthi uAhabi uzithobe phambi kwami? Ngenxa yokuthi ezithobile phambi kwami kangiyikuletha ububi ensukwini zakhe; ensukwini zendodana yakhe ngizaletha lobububi endlini yakhe\x + 2 Kho. 9.25.\x*.